{"tid":874322,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（假難民真犯罪）越南人蛇屯門搶灘　粵港聯合反偷渡拉27人","createTime":"2018-10-24T06:22:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-24T07:13:29.000Z","uid":167928,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0992deafb610858df8192f7a40a4dc0cacb181e9","tid":874322,"uid":167928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T06:22:21.000Z","msg":"粵港兩地執法部門展開代號「勇士行動」的反非法入境者行動，瓦解一個越南人蛇經內地偷渡來港的集團，共拘捕27人。 <br />\n<br />\n警方有組織罪案及三合會調查科，聯同水警小艇隊及刑事部探員、入境處，以及內地廣東省邊防總隊及廣東海警，昨晚(18日)趁人蛇集團安排一批越南籍偷渡客，經深圳水路由屯門搶灘，再安排車輛接送到旺角後，中港兩地警方隨即在兩地採取行動，其中本港警方拘捕16人，包括5男6女的集團骨幹成員（28歲至60歲），以及3男2女越南籍非法入境者（30歲至36歲）、2名內地女子，相信他們來港目的是做黑工。內地執法部門則拘捕11人，包括6名集團的骨幹成員，以及5名越南籍非法入境者。 <br />\n<br />\n行動中，警方在屯門截獲一艘5米長舢舨，並檢獲約10萬港元現金，以及一批手提電話，而舢舨上並沒有救生衣等設備。據警方有組織罪案及三合會調查科署理高級警司關競斌指出，人蛇集團分工精細，先由越南安排人蛇到深圳後，再以每位約1萬港元的偷渡費安排來港。蛇頭以車輛接載他們到市區匿藏，再一條龍式收取逾1,500港元提供偽造身份證，讓他們自行往酒樓或食肆做黑工。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/24/142155_e076f29a0a19a4696509342c6492b0d8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F24%2F142155_e076f29a0a19a4696509342c6492b0d8.png&h=3718e511&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/24/142156_c32c357448a681a8431a3fd80c50ab43.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F24%2F142156_c32c357448a681a8431a3fd80c50ab43.png&h=7175ed60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181019/mobile/bkn-20181019104449921-1019_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181019%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20181019104449921-1019_00822_001.html&d=XtradmV451CgdR%2FzWqTAF4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=ae9be9d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181019/mobile/bkn-20181019104449921-1019_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"27ddfbfeedad48b28fc29cbe573a5682dad38fa8","tid":874322,"uid":167928,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T06:22:59.000Z","msg":"屌你老母越南馬騮<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2640aae490d831478da34ac71a21ddb284d4a69d","tid":874322,"uid":167928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T06:25:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0ee28235852ed3cf3ff21c3366be3345f164287","tid":874322,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T06:25:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.destructoid.com/ul/291382-/ms3beach-noscale.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.destructoid.com%2Ful%2F291382-%2Fms3beach-noscale.jpg&h=368edb15&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bae61edf17750dde1a25f2be6f5bba8c2f8d0e78","tid":874322,"uid":167928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T06:29:16.000Z","msg":"重啓難民營 勞動班馬騮！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c2b9be9fb4c2e5a8320fbbdd5541a929e6cf73d","tid":874322,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T06:29:30.000Z","msg":"乜依家打緊越戰咩？"},{"pid":"bd49dc6b303ad3f661c8e7340e718b1e1ad96c94","tid":874322,"uid":167928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c2b9be9fb4c2e5a8320fbbdd5541a929e6cf73d","tid":874322,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T06:29:30.000Z","msg":"乜依家打緊越戰咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T06:35:13.